HEADWORD: Self-opinion
<hw>Self`-o*pin"ion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Opinion,
especially high opinion, of one's self; an overweening estimate of one's
self or of one's own opinion.</def> <rj><au>Collier.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

